sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as 前端 provider 模态
    participant API as admin.Handler
    participant Store as ProviderStore
    participant DB as SQLite
    participant Cfg as config.Config (启动加载)
    participant M as models.BuildProviderUsageView

    Note over Cfg: 启动时 Load() 读 provider_quota 段<br/>DefaultTokenLowRatio / DefaultCallLowRatio = 0.10

    rect rgb(235,245,255)
    Note over UI,DB: 配置阈值（创建 / 编辑 provider）
    UI->>API: PUT/POST /api/providers {monthly_token_low_ratio, monthly_call_low_ratio (比例)}
    API->>Store: CreateProvider / UpdateProvider(... ratio)
    Store->>DB: INSERT / UPDATE providers (两 REAL 列)
    DB-->>Store: ok
    Store-->>API: ProviderRecord (含两 ratio)
    API-->>UI: 200 + data
    end

    rect rgb(235,255,235)
    Note over API,M: 用量面板加载（effectiveRatio 解析）
    API->>Store: ListProviders()
    Store->>DB: SELECT ... monthly_token_low_ratio, monthly_call_low_ratio
    DB-->>Store: rows (含每 provider 覆盖值)
    Store-->>API: []ProviderRecord
    API->>M: BuildProviderUsageView(p, used, window, cfg.DefaultTokenLowRatio, cfg.DefaultCallLowRatio)
    M->>M: effToken = p.MonthlyTokenLowRatio>0 ? p.MonthlyTokenLowRatio : globalToken
    M->>M: effCall  = p.MonthlyCallLowRatio>0  ? p.MonthlyCallLowRatio  : globalCall
    M->>M: TokenLow = IsLowBalance(used, limit, effToken)
    M->>M: CallLow  = IsLowBalance(used, limit, effCall)
    M-->>API: ProviderUsageView { token_low, call_low }
    API-->>UI: GET /api/provider-usage -> data[]
    UI->>UI: renderUsageCell 读 token_low / call_low 布尔标红
    end
